Hey guys! Hope you all have the best Christmas with the ones you love! Wish you the best and I really hope you enjoy this time with your family, you know that this time of the year is one of the most magical! I will enjoy so much with my family, so i ask you to be patient because probably I'm not gonna post this days and I'm not gonna be so active! ENJOY ENJOY ♥️
MERRY CHRISTMAS 🎄

Chiara Ferragni's 2019 ♥️
An amazing year! So many good projects: Leo grew up, fashion weeks, magazine covers, dream travels, Chiara Ferragni Collection, The Blonde Salad, the premiers of Chiara Ferragni Unposted and so many more good things! Congrats for this amazing year, proud of you @chiaraferragni !!
